## Response Shape

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Resources retrieved successfully",
  "data": {
    "resources": [...],
    "pagination": {
      "page": 1, "limit": 100, "total": 51,
      "totalPages": 1, "hasNext": false, "hasPrevious": false
    }
  }
}
```

